SECTION 1. The following barrios are hereby created in the Municipality of Sta. Margarita, Province of Samar:

Barrio Salvacion, consisting of the sitios of Hemaangno, Tina, Kinabugsohan, Pana-awan, and Bungnog;

Barrio Roxas, consisting of the sitio of Panogoran, Misikpisik and Cadigamhon;

Barrio Sundra, consisting of the sitios of Naporo and Pasig;

Barrio Solsogon, consisting of the sitios of Cagbatilisan, Da-o, Cagsumhi, Calirangan, Nabura-West, Tigdaraja, Canmeriu and Mahabol;

Barrio Bahay, consisting of the sitios of Panlulogayan, Canhurao, Pamamaliwlan and Minorosan;

Barrio Bana-ao, consisting of the sitios of Laboyao, Macatol, Cabariwan, Sinagoksokan, Kinarangdangan and Pasongon;

Barrio Agrupacion, consisting of the sitio of Anoling;

Barrio Arapison, consisting of the sitios of Bañgon, Illawod, Guincatolan Magcahibang and Campagote;

Barrio Victory, consisting of the sitios of Hinaango, Lotang, Canati-an, Logos, Macalayalaya, Cahanagdoñgan and Ombo-bo;

Barrio Caasloman, consisting of the sitios of Heogba, Natopo, Capudlosan, Cabacongan and Tibobnot;

Barrio Burabod, consisting of the sitio of Caglagting, Epil, Malicolico and Canloncas;

Barrio Burabod, consisting of the sitio of Caglagting, Epil, Malicolico and Canloncas;

Barrio Nabulo, consisting of the sitios of Tibalad, Napuliron, Dalakit, Canamailom and Bakung;

Barrio Mahayag, consisting of the sitios of Aliat, Pañgalaw-an, Panihwan, Capantapan, Hecaloty, MaloyaPayo, Barayong and Cabatuan;

Barrio Inoragyao, consisting of the sitios of Guinharan, Kabulo-Sur, Agusip, Canmalon, Pinarnaliwan and Capinyahan;

Barrio Mabuhay, consisting of the sitios of Cantomas, Mueblo, Castillano and Cangkokong;

Barrio Lambao, consisting of the sitios of Da-o, Nabora and Restituloriwa;

Barrio Moroporo, consisting of the sitios of Lininti-an and Magcayongod;

Barrio Campeig, consisting of the sitios of Canba-nog, Sosocon, Alao and Felehan;

Barrio Canipulan, consisting of the sitios of Cantimbang, Cancapilong and Cangodio;

Barrio Gajo, consisting of the sitios of Malolonod, Guinbologo-an Canbanog and Biad;

Barrio Panaro-an consisting of the sitio of Kinabogsocan, Cambanog and Caninaria;

Barrio Perito, consisting of the sitios of Tinbobonot, Honoapan and Caboago-an;

Barrio Perito, consisting of the sitios of Tinbobonot, Honoapan and Caboago-an;

Barrio Palale, consisting of the sitios of Magdodilot, Saquib, Guinsohayan, Pangpang, Lobtong and Cataynazan; and

Barrio Caganahao, consisting of the sitios of Pangogob-an, Lumaras and Hindang.
